{"tid":1378922,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"倉鼠咬籠，點算","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T17:20:01.000Z","uid":259434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0579b2fe757b25f364d09e0ad72636e7b03e7d02","tid":1378922,"uid":259434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:02:08.000Z","msg":"我係新人，養左隻銀孤，都養左成兩個月，因為一伸手，就比佢追住咬，所以唔敢同佢接觸。<br />\n<br />\n最近幾日，佢開始咬籠，咬到個籠既漆都甩埋，上網睇話倉鼠需要自由，所以咬籠。依家好擔心，應該點做？放佢出嚟俾佢玩，我又驚佢走失。又唔敢捉返返入籠。"},{"pid":"34cadd70cd614f44ac0a688c4be4e43df1d25e9a","tid":1378922,"uid":56199,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:06:53.000Z","msg":"唔識養唔好養，還佢自由啦"},{"pid":"a619c5468160bcb7fbcc146dd5f8ea387d193811","tid":1378922,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:30:56.000Z","msg":"用水"},{"pid":"8891e7035dba9a1faf232fd58785176b9ee9008c","tid":1378922,"uid":56954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:36:39.000Z","msg":"我以前係由得個寵開住等佢通房走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢係出面玩到悶自己就識返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你同隻鼠熟落下先啦<br />\n用野食引佢, 等佢記自你陣味, 到佢對你冇咁有戒心就抱佢上手掃佢d毛等佢有安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a95d443477370796b5882c887d9cbf00d33e9f","tid":1378922,"uid":227275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:37:25.000Z","msg":"727 728 打人合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6N677ZNEHyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6N677ZNEHyo&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL%2FkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=b6ec8b6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6N677ZNEHyo</a>"},{"pid":"8c086b3893b0f17135e1e6e9916589ca31358c57","tid":1378922,"uid":130665,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"倉鼠咬籠大多數有2個原因<br />\n1. 個籠嘅活動範圍唔夠大<br />\n2. 個跑輪太大/太細佢跑唔到<br 